OL,4,G1330FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GAt The Queens Hotel in Harlech,
OL,6,     GRachel and professional
OL,7,     Gimpersonator Liam are keen to
OL,8,     Gmake a good impression. But an
OL,9,     Gissue in the bathroom gives one
OL,10,     GB&Ber that sinking feeling.
OL,11,G1400FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GFor the third visit of the week,
OL,13,     Gthe B&Bers head to Mat and
OL,14,     GHelen's B&B, The Mill at Glynhir
OL,15,     Gin Llandybie, Carmarthenshire,
OL,16,     Gwhere things get prickly during a
OL,17,     Gvisit to a botanical garden.
