OL,4,G1430FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe final visit is to Lesley and
OL,6,     GSarah's Hideaway Escapes in
OL,7,     GPembrokeshire, where one set of
OL,8,     Gguests' decision to sleep in
OL,9,     Gtheir car rather than their room
OL,10,     Gleaves the hosts all revved up.
OL,11,G1505FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GOn a feisty payment day, the
OL,13,     GB&Bers tackle everything from
OL,14,     Gbathroom blues to one set of
OL,15,     Gguests completely refusing to try
OL,16,     Gout one of their rivals' rooms.
OL,17,     GBut who'll win the week?
